- App theme is defined in `theme/Theme.kt` as a light-only Material3 scheme
- Custom colors live in `theme/Color.kt`

## Resources

- Use Compose Multiplatform resources (`composeResources/`) for strings, drawables, fonts
- Access via generated accessors (e.g., `Res.string.*`, `Res.drawable.*`)
